{"tid":2279921,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[第二屆OMDB造句大賽] 帶來很大痛苦","createTime":"2020-11-10T06:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T06:35:23.000Z","uid":64078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f3b64bbdd0002f4953c1baba3b6777ba0a3ec2c9","tid":2279921,"uid":64078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T06:33:41.000Z","msg":"公民黨黨魁楊岳橋則表示，北京短時間內兩次大動作取議員資格，是對港人及整個制度的侮辱，<span class=\"red\">亦證明民主派議員留守議會，為北京帶來很大的痛苦</span>。他指「第一次DQ是荒謬，第二次DQ不會變得合理」，反映作為國際金融中心的香港容不下反對的聲音<br />\n<br />\n請巴打們發揮創意，希望唔好為OMDB帶來咁大痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0998a42ba5a368c217158ee1e54a707e9c1a509","tid":2279921,"uid":140218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T06:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VJOwiGc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVJOwiGc.png&h=2cb342bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cde7acfa3d6218ce2529dd765165a0f36c7739","tid":2279921,"uid":64078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T06:35:23.000Z","msg":"三文魚唔食日本人，為蔡瀾帶來很大痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}